  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Food for Thought- Feed Schoolchildren in Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In the US, many of us take basic education and a hot meal for granted. At MCF, our goal is to provide these necessities to Ugandan children, one school at a time. Our innovative 10:30 porridge program addresses the underlying cause of low attendance &amp; high dropout rates by providing a hot meal a day for schoolchildren. Using this approach, we give parents an immediate, tangible reason to keep their children enrolled, while at the same time &quot;providing a means &amp; belief in self to escape poverty.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
